# Configuration for RipGrep https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep/
# Part of https://github.com/DustinVenegas/dotfiles/

# Truncate what can be vomited out
--max-columns=160

# Ignore .git folders
--glob=!.git/*

# Ignore .git folders (Windows)
--glob=!.git\*

# Ignore case, unless the input contains cased characters
--smart-case
